\n\r\n<p>Interested and qualified candidates should send their CV to:&nbsp;<strong><a href=\"mailto:Corpers@geekhub.com.ng\">Corpers@geekhub.com.ng</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong>using the Job title as the subject of the mail.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'https://www.myjobmag.com/job/youth-corps-member-web-designer-geekhub-nigeria', NULL, 0, NULL, 'active', 'MyJobMag', '2026-02-11 17:56:24', '2026-02-16 07:49:24', 1, 'youth-corps-member-web-designer-at-geekhub-nigeria', 1, NULL, NULL, 1, 1, NULL, NULL),
