\n\r\n<p>Interested and qualified candidates should send their CV to:&nbsp;<strong><a href=\"mailto:Corpers@geekhub.com.ng\">Corpers@geekhub.com.ng</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong>using the Job title as the subject of the mail.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'https://www.myjobmag.com/job/youth-corps-member-web-designer-geekhub-nigeria', NULL, 0, NULL, 'active', 'MyJobMag', '2026-02-11 17:59:16', '2026-02-16 07:49:24', 1, 'youth-corps-member-web-designer-at-geekhub-nigeria', 1, NULL, NULL, 1, 1, NULL, NULL),
(10, 'c6d33c78-3c4b-4c09-8d14-4a51010cd33f', 'Youth Corps Member (Web Designer) at GeekHub Nigeria', 'GeekHub Nigeria', 0, NULL, 'storage/logos/zyMoTL9czEE42EdjlcJXXWropgcFLqFKGbCUAGIx.png', 1, 'full-time', 'Abuja, Nigeria', 'entry', NULL, '<p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>We are seeking young, vibrant, result driven Youth Corp Members to serve with us,as their place of primary assignment.</li>\r\n	<li>We are looking for NYSC members to fill the position of:</li>\r\n	<li>Web Designer: The Web Designer will be responsible for creating visually appealing and user-friendly websites, ensuring proper functionality, and implementing design principles to enhance the user experience.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Desired Skills and Attributes</strong><br />\r\nWeb Designer:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Proven experience as a Web Developer, demonstrating proficiency in HTML, CSS, JavaScript, and other web technologies.</li>\r\n	<li>Strong understanding of responsive web design, cross-browser compatibility, and web accessibility standards.</li>\r\n	<li>Experience with front-end frameworks/libraries (e.g., Bootstrap, React, Vue.js) and back-end languages/frameworks (e.g., PHP, Python, Node.js) is preferred.</li>\r\n	<li>Proficiency in version control systems (e.g., Git) and web development tools (e.g., IDEs, Code Igniter, Laravel, package managers) is a plus.</li>\r\n	<li>Strong Back end integration frameworks and database management using technologies like MYSQL, PHP</li>\r\n	<li>Attention to detail</li>\r\n	<li>Understanding of user experience (UX) principles</li>\r\n	<li>Proficient in use of AI vibe coding to create Websites landing pages and applications</li>\r\n	<li>Proficient in the use of LLMs like ChatGPT, Google Gemini, etc</li>\r\n	<li>Ability to work with design software (e.g., Figma, Adobe Photoshop, Illustrator), problem-solving skills</li>\r\n	<li>Time management skills.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Method of Application&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Interested and qualified candidates should send their CV to:&nbsp;<strong><a href=\"mailto:Corpers@geekhub.com.ng\">Corpers@geekhub.com.ng</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong>using the Job title as the subject of the mail.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'https://www.myjobmag.com/job/youth-corps-member-web-designer-geekhub-nigeria', NULL, 0, NULL, 'active', 'MyJobMag', '2026-02-11 18:00:23', '2026-02-16 07:49:25', 0, 'youth-corps-member-web-designer-at-geekhub-nigeria', 1, NULL, NULL, 1, 1, NULL, NULL),
(11, 'eedc3ccf-b5ac-4338-98c7-e3ad06d2eb97', 'Web Engineer at LemFi (Formerly Lemonade Finance)', 'LemFi', 1, '<p>Lemonade Finance (YC S21) is building a neobank for immigrants in North America &amp; Europe. We provide our users with multi-currency accounts that allow them to hold, send, and receive money from Africa in any currency for their business and personal banking needs.</p>', 'storage/logos/JmfKhxR1OdArlXF5muDwStEeqBbCU7YD75ce5XbD.png', 4, 'full-time', 'Lagos, Nigeria', 'mid', NULL, '<p><strong>The Role</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>You will be a full-stack engineer with main focus on Frontend working on LemFi&rsquo;s operational &quot;brain&quot;, designing the internal software that automates our most critical financial processes. Your mission is to transform complex, high-volume back-office tasks like payments operations, fraud investigations, and regulatory reporting into streamlined, front-end functionality.</li>\r\n	<li>You won&rsquo;t just be building tools; you&rsquo;ll create efficient internal interfaces that empower our operations teams to move faster and with greater precision. By embedding AI and agentic automation into every workflow, you&rsquo;ll ensure that managing global money movement is as intelligent and effortless as the user experience it supports.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>How You&#39;ll Contribute</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Build &amp; Ship: Design and deliver high-quality, scalable web features using Vue.js, with a strong focus on efficiency, security, and maintainability.</li>\r\n	<li>Own the Experience: Take end-to-end responsibility for features from technical design and implementation to testing, deployment, and production support.</li>\r\n	<li>BFF Development: Implement and maintain backend-for-frontend logic in TypeScript, shaping APIs and data models that serve the needs of the web client efficiently and securely.</li>\r\n	<li>Ensure Reliability: Uphold high engineering standards through automated testing, clean code practices, and proactive monitoring of frontend and BFF services.</li>\r\n	<li>Drive Cross-Functional Impact: Collaborate closely with Product, Design, and Backend teams to deliver compliant, customer-centric financial experiences aligned with regulatory requirements.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Who You Are</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Impact-Driven: You focus on delivering meaningful user and business outcomes, not just shipping features.</li>\r\n	<li>Technically Grounded: You have strong experience building business-oriented web applications and are comfortable working with TypeScript on the backend for BFF logic.</li>\r\n	<li>High Ownership: You take responsibility for your work from concept through production and continuously look for ways to improve what you&rsquo;ve built.</li>\r\n	<li>Collaborative: You communicate clearly with Product, Design, and Engineering, valuing shared success over individual credit.</li>\r\n	<li>Curious: You actively seek feedback and stay up to date with modern frontend patterns, AI tooling, and best practices.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>What You&#39;ll Bring</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Experience building production web apps with Vue.js &amp; Nuxt.js</li>\r\n	<li>Strong TypeScript skills, including BFF development</li>\r\n	<li>Proficient in JavaScript, HTML, CSS, SASS</li>\r\n	<li>Experience working with and shaping REST APIs</li>\r\n	<li>Solid understanding of modern frontend architecture, state management &amp; performance optimisation</li>\r\n	<li>Familiar with Git, testing frameworks (Jest/Mocha), build tools &amp; CI/CD</li>\r\n	<li>Working knowledge of cloud environments &amp; Docker</li>\r\n	<li>Hands-on experience using LLMs for coding and daily workflows</li>\r\n</ul>', 'https://www.myjobmag.com/job/web-engineer-lemonade-finance-yc-s21', NULL, 0, NULL, 'active', 'MyJobMag', '2026-02-11 18:09:22', '2026-02-16 07:49:25', 0, 'web-engineer-at-lemfi-formerly-lemonade-finance', 1, NULL, NULL, 1, 1, NULL, NULL),
(12, '8435d96f-9e4a-4e1f-9702-765653bf18bf', 'Fullstack Developer (PHP Laravel + ReactJS)', 'GoodTenants', 1, '<p>GoodTenants.io is a PropTech platform helping landlords, property managers, and tenants manage properties more efficiently. We provide tools for property operations, tenant communication, task and issue management, reporting, and data-driven insights, helping real estate businesses save time, reduce costs, and improve tenant experience</p>', 'storage/logos/6d4gS6h34z7zZcdfCcZWpOtMBoezroK14FEkQQJ4.jpg', 1, 'full-time', 'Lagos, Nigeria', 'senior', '300,000 - 400,000/month', '<p>We are looking for a Fullstack Developer (PHP Laravel + React) to help build, maintain, and scale our property management platform. You will work across backend APIs and frontend interfaces, contributing directly to features used by landlords, property managers, and tenants.<br />\r\nThis role is remote, but open to candidates based in Nigeria only.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Responsibilities</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Backend (Laravel):</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Develop and maintain RESTful APIs using Laravel</li>\r\n	<li>Work with databases (MySQL/PostgreSQL), migrations, and Eloquent ORM</li>\r\n	<li>Implement authentication, roles, and permissions</li>\r\n	<li>Optimize performance, security, and scalability</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Frontend (React):</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Build modern, responsive user interfaces with React</li>\r\n	<li>Consume APIs and manage application state</li>\r\n	<li>Collaborate with designers and product team to deliver clean UX</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>General:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Write clean, maintainable, and testable code</li>\r\n	<li>Participate in code reviews and sprint planning</li>\r\n	<li>Debug, improve, and refactor existing features</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Proven experience with&nbsp;<strong>Laravel</strong>&nbsp;(API-driven applications)</li>\r\n	<li>Strong experience with&nbsp;<strong>React</strong>&nbsp;(hooks, components, routing)</li>\r\n	<li>Solid understanding of REST APIs</li>\r\n	<li>Experience with relational databases (MySQL or PostgreSQL)</li>\r\n	<li>Familiarity with Git and collaborative workflows</li>\r\n	<li>Ability to work independently in a remote environment</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Nice to Have</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Tailwind CSS or similar CSS frameworks</li>\r\n	<li>TypeScript</li>\r\n	<li>Experience working on SaaS products</li>\r\n	<li>Knowledge of property management or fintech systems</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>What We Offer</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Competitive pay</li>\r\n	<li>Hybrid work</li>\r\n	<li>Flexible working hours</li>\r\n	<li>Opportunity to work on a growing PropTech platform</li>\r\n	<li>Small, collaborative, impact-driven team</li>\r\n</ul>', 'https://api-uat.goodtenants.io/speed-test', NULL, 0, NULL, 'active', 'MyJobMag', '2026-02-14 02:16:27', '2026-02-16 07:49:25', 0, 'fullstack-developer-php-laravel-reactjs', 1, NULL, NULL, 1, 1, NULL, NULL),
(13, 'eef60fc9-f54d-4eb3-998d-bbeb6d73196a', 'IT Sales Account Manager at Alfred & Victoria Associates', 'Alfred & Victoria Associates', 1, '<p>Alfred &amp; Victoria Associates is one of Nigeria&rsquo;s leading ICT solution based company. Our company offers a wide range of services which are in high demand of today&rsquo;s emerging market.</p>', 'storage/logos/DJjvRCn6QXqWdzmaf3bQOkXUvEQg7rGZje41dKNv.jpg', 1, 'full-time', 'Lagos, Nigeria', 'senior', NULL, '<p><strong>Job Purpose</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>The purpose of this job role is to create long term relationships with the portfolio of assigned customers.</li>\r\n	<li>The role serves to understand the customer&#39;s demands, plan on how to meet these demands, and generate sales for the company as a result.</li>\r\n	<li>The job role ensures the sales of the company&rsquo;s products and services within a defined line of business (LOB). Ensures consistent, profitable growth in sales revenues within the LOB through execution of agreed sales strategies.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Generate sales for a portfolio of accounts and reach the company&#39;s sales target</li>\r\n	<li>Identify new sales opportunities within existing accounts to maintain a client-account manager relationship by up-selling and cross-selling</li>\r\n	<li>Attending client&rsquo;s meetings</li>\r\n	<li>Preparation of Proposal, bids and quotes</li>\r\n	<li>Participate in all sales meetings along with attendance of Tech shows as required</li>\r\n	<li>Ensure excellent customer satisfaction working with customers</li>\r\n	<li>Provide feedback from customers and ensure resolution of issues (if any).</li>\r\n	<li>Maintain and update customer contact records</li>\r\n	<li>Identify/manage and escalate/solve conflicts with clients</li>\r\n	<li>Interact and coordinate with the sales team and other staff members in</li>\r\n	<li>other departments working on the same account</li>\r\n	<li>Identify clients&rsquo; budgets</li>\r\n	<li>Meet targets and deadlines for accounts</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Key Result Area:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Achievement of the LOB&rsquo;s sales target</li>\r\n	<li>Maintain a good working relationship with team members.</li>\r\n	<li>A satisfied clientele portfolio</li>\r\n	<li>A cordial and efficient synergy between the sales team and the technical team</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Experience &amp; Education Requirements</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>A minimum qualification of First Degree in any related field.</li>\r\n	<li>A minimum of 4 years in sales role in an active capacity (IT Sector)</li>\r\n	<li>Experience in a target-driven environment is an added advantage</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Knowledge Requirements:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Market Knowledge</li>\r\n	<li>Product/Solutions Knowledge</li>\r\n	<li>Customers&rsquo; knowledge</li>\r\n	<li>Competition&rsquo;s knowledge</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Skill Requirements:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Negotiation skills</li>\r\n	<li>Good prospecting skills</li>\r\n	<li>Rapport building on skill</li>\r\n	<li>Active listening skill</li>\r\n	<li>Effective communication skills</li>\r\n	<li>Presentation skills</li>\r\n	<li>Effective writing skills</li>\r\n	<li>Relationship management skills</li>\r\n	<li>A passion for selling</li>\r\n	<li>Negotiation skills</li>\r\n	<li>Leadership skills</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Method of Application</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Interested and qualified candidates should send their tailored CV to:&nbsp;<strong>apply@alfred-victoria</strong>.<strong>com&nbsp;</strong>using the Job title as the subject of the email.</p>', 'https://www.myjobmag.com/job/it-sales-account-manager-alfred-amp-victoria-associates', NULL, 0, NULL, 'active', 'MyJobMag', '2026-02-14 02:39:11', '2026-02-16 07:49:25', 0, 'it-sales-account-manager-at-alfred-victoria-associates', 1, NULL, NULL, 1, 1, NULL, NULL),
(14, 'b96408c7-cd8c-4e5f-a29d-12ab247564ab', 'Digital Marketing Specialist at Campus Technologies Limited', 'Campus Technologies Limited', 1, '<p>Campus Technologies Limited is a multi-product consulting firm that provides Information Technology consulting services across various industry sectors. We are a provider of Information Management and Technology solutions in Nigeria providing solutions that enable individuals and organizations to transform their businesses. Our clients are varied; they include large, small and medium sized businesses, governmental and non-governmental institutions, agencies and departments. Campus Technologies Limited is an indegenous company with international affiliations with world-class Solution &amp; Service providing organizations such as NIIT India. We help our clients identify, implement, and manage modern technologies.</p>', 'storage/logos/3SOxu0UuGMyvDhRcnl5pn92XWYXqtiB9jXluoef1.jpg', 1, 'full-time', 'Abuja, Nigeria', 'mid', NULL, '<p><strong>Description</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Campus Technologies Limited&nbsp;is seeking a creative and results-driven Digital Marketing Specialist to plan, implement, and manage our online marketing strategies.</li>\r\n	<li>The ideal candidate will be responsible for increasing brand awareness, generating leads, driving engagement across digital platforms, and supporting business growth through effective digital campaigns.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Develop and execute digital marketing campaigns across social media, email, website, and search platforms.</li>\r\n	<li>Create engaging content for social media, website, and email marketing.</li>\r\n	<li>Manage and grow the company&rsquo;s social media presence.</li>\r\n	<li>Run paid online advertising campaigns (Facebook, Instagram, Google Ads, etc.).</li>\r\n	<li>Optimize website content for SEO to improve online visibility.</li>\r\n	<li>Track, analyze, and report on campaign performance and audience engagement.</li>\r\n	<li>Generate leads through online strategies and follow up with prospective clients.</li>\r\n	<li>Manage email marketing campaigns and subscriber lists.</li>\r\n	<li>Monitor digital trends and recommend new marketing opportunities.</li>\r\n	<li>Collaborate with internal teams to align marketing efforts with business goals.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Requirements &amp; Qualifications</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Bachelor&rsquo;s degree in relevant fields</li>\r\n	<li>Proven experience in digital marketing or social media management.</li>\r\n	<li>Knowledge of SEO, SEM, and online advertising tools.</li>\r\n	<li>Proficiency in social media platforms and content creation tools.</li>\r\n	<li>Strong writing and communication skills.</li>\r\n	<li>Creativity, multitasking, and attention to detail.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Key Skills:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Social Media Management</li>\r\n	<li>Content Creation</li>\r\n	<li>SEO &amp; SEM</li>\r\n	<li>Email Marketing</li>\r\n	<li>Graphic Design (Canva or similar tools)</li>\r\n	<li>Customer Engagement.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Benefits</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Opportunity to work in a dynamic tech-driven environment</li>\r\n	<li>Career growth and training opportunities</li>\r\n	<li>Supportive and collaborative team.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Method of Application</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Interested and qualified candidates should send their CV to:&nbsp;<strong>hr@campustechng.com</strong>&nbsp;using the Job Title as the subject of the mail.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Note</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Only candidates who meet the requirements will be contacted for the next stage of the selection process. We look forward to having passionate and skilled professionals join our team!.</li>\r\n	<li>If you are passionate about networking, have a strong desire to educate the next generation of network professionals, and possess the required qualifications, we invite you to join our institute as a CCNA Instructor.</li>\r\n	<li>Help shape the future of networking and be a part of a rewarding educational journey.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'https://www.myjobmag.com/job/digital-marketing-specialist-campus-technologies-limited-1', NULL, 0, NULL, 'active', 'MyJobMag', '2026-02-14 11:49:46', '2026-02-16 07:49:25', 0, 'digital-marketing-specialist-at-campus-technologies-limited', 1, NULL, NULL, 1, 1, NULL, NULL),
(15, '52b8bb19-5070-4221-9c58-0f27f610906c', 'Data Center Critical Facilities Engineer at Equinix Nigeria', 'Equinix', 1, '<p>Equinix is the world&rsquo;s digital infrastructure company&reg;, operating over 260 data centers across the globe. Digital leaders harness Equinix&#39;s trusted platform to bring together and interconnect foundational infrastructure at software speed. Equinix enables organizations to access all the right places, partners and possibilities to scale with agility, speed the launch of digital services, deliver world-class experiences and multiply their value, while supporting their sustainability goals.</p>', 'storage/logos/BSabmkDKhAUhFHzQ7bT6geHxGHl6cOIskdhjskXK.jpg', 1, 'full-time', 'Lagos, Nigeria', 'mid', NULL, '<p>Job ID:&nbsp;JR-158357</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Applies acquired job skills to work on tasks that are semi-routine in nature. Focus is on semi-routine tasks within standard operating procedures.</li>\r\n	<li>Supports the overall team.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Responsibilities</strong><br />\r\nFacility/Infrastructure Maintenance:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Performs semi-routine preventative maintence checks on-site to non-critical, facility components</li>\r\n	<li>Performs semi-routine repairs, maintenance and installations to non-critical facility components</li>\r\n	<li>Monitors the Builiding Monitoring System (BMS) and responds timely to semi-routine alarms according to standard operating procedures</li>\r\n	<li>Assists more senior staff in higher facility repairs and corrective maintenance measures</li>\r\n	<li>Operates plumbing, fire suppression, and safety systems, under the supervision of more senior technical staff</li>\r\n	<li>Normally follows established procedures on routine work, requires instructions only on new assignments.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Vendor Support:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Coordinates with vendors to ensure maintenance activities are carried out as per Equinix&#39;s requirements</li>\r\n	<li>Supports the work order approval process for service providers on routine maintenance work, for tracking: briefing at the start of work, work during the day workday/shift and final review of the work carried out</li>\r\n	<li>Ensures vendor maintenance activities are carried out as per Equinix&#39;s standard operating procedures.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Site Administration &amp; Incident Support:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Performs semi-routine site logs for permits, such as Maintenance Operation Protocol (MOPs) and scripts</li>\r\n	<li>Uses acquired job skills in following operating procedures to support on-site administration.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Work Orders &amp; Additional Projects:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Completes semi-routine work requests and circuit installations</li>\r\n	<li>Follows established procedures with troubleshooting and maintaining office equipment (if necessary); supports auxiliary equipment and machines</li>\r\n	<li>Assists more senior staff with responding on-site incidents and acts as directed.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Collaboration:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Collaborates with others to resolve semi-routine facility incidents</li>\r\n	<li>Provides assistance to more senior staff on infrastructure projects</li>\r\n	<li>Informs stakeholders of inventory needs to maintain stock levels of parts and equipment.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Qualifications</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Electrical and Electronics Engineering or related degree required</li>\r\n	<li>1-4 years of equivalent work experience.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'https://careers.equinix.com/jobs/data-center-critical-facilities-engineer-lagos-nigeria-020c2018-a83b-46b7-bcd8-06eb7d129b78?&utm_source=MyJobMag', NULL, 0, NULL, 'active', 'MyJobMag', '2026-02-14 12:10:21', '2026-02-16 07:49:25', 0, 'data-center-critical-facilities-engineer-at-equinix-nigeria', 1, NULL, NULL, 1, 1, NULL, NULL),
(16, '49d379be-6bdf-4532-bbc4-f4d50b5b7642', 'Full Stack Engineer', 'AnyWorkY', 1, '<p>IT, software engineering, Internet</p>', 'storage/logos/D4HwdvuHa2FLv1tJkVZIkEohF38g5yMO430GiQan.png', 1, 'contract', 'Abuja, Nigeria', 'senior', NULL, '<p>Position : Full Stack Engineer - Abuja</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We&rsquo;re looking for a&nbsp;<strong>Full Stack Engineer</strong>&nbsp;to help build and scale Anyworky&rsquo;s core platform. You&rsquo;ll work across the frontend and backend to ship production features that directly impact customers and providers.<br />\r\nThis role is hands-on and ownership-driven. You&rsquo;ll design, build, deploy, and improve features end-to-end &mdash; not just maintain existing code.<br />\r\n<strong>What You&rsquo;ll Do</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Build and maintain full-stack features across mobile and backend services</li>\r\n	<li>Design and implement REST APIs and service integrations</li>\r\n	<li>Work on real-time marketplace flows (booking, matching, payments, notifications)</li>\r\n	<li>Integrate third-party services (e.g. Stripe, background checks, messaging)</li>\r\n	<li>Improve system scalability, performance, and reliability</li>\r\n	<li>Collaborate closely with product, design, and operations</li>\r\n	<li>Take features from idea &rarr; production &rarr; iteration</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Technical Environment</strong>&nbsp;(You don&rsquo;t need everything, but experience in several is important)</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Backend: Node.js / Express, REST APIs, event-driven services</li>\r\n	<li>Frontend / Mobile: Flutter or modern JS frameworks</li>\r\n	<li>Payments: Stripe (escrow, payouts, webhooks)</li>\r\n	<li>Databases: MongoDB / PostgreSQL</li>\r\n	<li>Messaging / events: Redis, queues, pub/sub</li>\r\n	<li>Cloud: AWS / Azure / GCP</li>\r\n	<li>Containers &amp; deployment: Docker (Kubernetes is a plus)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Nice to Have</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Experience with marketplace or on-demand platforms</li>\r\n	<li>Experience with mobile-first products</li>\r\n	<li>Familiarity with CI/CD and cloud infrastructure</li>\r\n	<li>Startup or fast-paced product environment experience</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Why Join Anyworky</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>High ownership and real impact</li>\r\n	<li>Work on meaningful, real-world problems</li>\r\n	<li>No bureaucracy &mdash; decisions move fast</li>\r\n	<li>Remote-friendly and outcome-driven culture</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Required profile for job ad : Full Stack Engineer - Abuja</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Strong experience in full-stack development</li>\r\n	<li>Solid software engineering fundamentals</li>\r\n	<li>Comfortable debugging and optimizing production systems</li>\r\n	<li>Experience building or scaling real products (startups or product teams)</li>\r\n	<li>Ability to work independently and take ownership</li>\r\n	<li>Clear communicator in a remote team environment</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Job criteria for job ad : Full Stack Engineer - Abuja</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;<strong>Job category</strong>&nbsp;:&nbsp;IT, new technologies</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;<strong>Industries</strong>&nbsp;:&nbsp;IT, software engineering, Internet</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Employment type</strong>&nbsp;:&nbsp;Fixed-term contract</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Region&nbsp;</strong>:&nbsp;Abuja</li>\r\n	<li><strong>City&nbsp;</strong>:&nbsp;Abuja</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;<strong>Remote work</strong>&nbsp;:&nbsp;Yes</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Experience level</strong>&nbsp;:&nbsp;2 to 5 years - 5 to 10 years - More than 10 years</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Educational level&nbsp;</strong>:&nbsp;HND - Bachelor - Master - Doctorate</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Spoken language</strong>&nbsp;:&nbsp;english &gt; fluent</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Number of Position(s)</strong>&nbsp;:&nbsp;1</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;<strong>Team management</strong>&nbsp;:&nbsp;No</li>\r\n</ul>', 'https://www.nigeriajob.com/job-vacancies-nigeria/full-stack-engineer-abuja-226191?utm_campaign=google_jobs_apply&utm_source=google_jobs_apply&utm_medium=organic', NULL, 0, NULL, 'active', 'Nigeria Job', '2026-02-14 12:29:36', '2026-02-16 07:49:25', 0, 'full-stack-engineer', 1, NULL, NULL, 1, 1, NULL, NULL),
(17, 'a99e7bf0-9080-45f1-a7bc-12f4d5cbabf1', 'Updated Position', 'Test Company', 0, NULL, NULL, 1, 'full-time', 'Remote', NULL, NULL, 'Test description', 'https://example.com', NULL, 0, NULL, 'active', NULL, '2026-02-16 08:18:58', '2026-02-16 08:18:59', 0, 'test-position', 1, NULL, NULL, 1, 1, NULL, NULL),
(18, '82d2f312-f609-4dac-98b8-19a2b0a4aa2a', 'Marketing & Sales Relations Officer', 'Nativedge', 1, NULL, NULL, 1, 'full-time', 'Lagos, Nigeria', 'senior', '250,000', '<p>Supports client acquisition, relationship management, and revenue growth initiatives.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Responsibilities</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Prospect and qualify leads</li>\r\n	<li>Maintain client communication records</li>\r\n	<li>Support proposal documentation</li>\r\n	<li>Ensure alignment with company policies</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Requirements</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Bachelor&#39;s degree in Marketing, Business Administration, Economics, or related field</li>\r\n	<li>Minimum 2+ years sales or marketing experience</li>\r\n	<li>Strong communication and interpersonal skills</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Compensation</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>₦250,000 monthly salary</li>\r\n	<li>5% commission on revenue successfully generated</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Job Type: Full-time</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Pay: From ₦250,000.00 per month</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Experience:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>sales or marketing: 2 years (Required)</li>\r\n</ul>', 'https://open.app.jobrapido.com/ng/5338654753486274560?oc=sponsored&uuid=ngF0019c9cb6303622aa', NULL, 0, NULL, 'active', 'employer', '2026-02-27 00:47:48', '2026-03-02 23:16:43', 0, 'marketing-sales-relations-officer', 1, NULL, NULL, 1, 4, NULL, NULL),
(19, '128a034c-b608-4c2b-a97f-f699481c1723', 'Web Developer', 'Nativedge', 1, '<p>Testing</p>', NULL, 1, 'full-time', 'Abuja, Nigeria', 'mid', '250,000', '<p>Testing Testing..</p>', 'https://example.com/apply', NULL, 0, NULL, 'active', 'employer', '2026-02-27 01:10:03', '2026-03-01 16:46:51', 0, 'web-developer', 1, NULL, NULL, 1, 4, NULL, NULL),
(20, 'b5a5543c-36eb-44bb-afad-2073bc541596', 'Frontend Developer', 'Nativedge', 1, '<p>Sopdap is a renowned service provider for all kinds of ICT Services. We develop Software and Web applications that has been successful in meeting customer demands and upholding the company&rsquo;s profiles in the world of ICT solutions.</p>', NULL, 1, 'full-time', 'Abuja, Nigeria', 'mid', '250,000', '<p>&quot;Sopdap is a renowned service provider for all kinds of ICT Services. We develop Software and Web applications that has been successful in meeting customer demands and upholding the company&rsquo;s profiles in the world of ICT solutions. We have professionals with extensive experience and also the latest/efficient tools for offering the best solutions at the moment. Our Best Features Are: Website Design, Web &amp; Mobile Application Development, Digital Marketing, SEO, eCommerce Development, Training and General Consultancy. Contact us today: We are the solution you have been waiting for.&quot;</p>', 'https://example.com/apply', NULL, 0, NULL, 'active', 'employer', '2026-02-27 01:39:25', '2026-03-01 15:06:45', 0, 'frontend-developer', 1, NULL, NULL, 1, 4, NULL, NULL),
(21, 'e846df9f-3547-4921-99e7-029d6a4d972a', 'jksdj', 'Nativedge', 1, '<p>jkdfdfkdlkfdkfdf</p>', NULL, 1, 'full-time', 'Abuja, Nigeria', 'entry', '250,000', '<p>dsdsdsd</p>', 'https://example.com/apply', NULL, 0, NULL, 'active', 'employer', '2026-02-27 01:43:14', '2026-03-01 10:31:17', 0, 'jksdj', 1, NULL, NULL, 1, 4, NULL, NULL),
